<headline>Winter Storm Watch issued January 27 at 3:08PM EST until January 30 at 12:00AM EST by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...WINTER STORM WATCH IN EFFECT FROM LATE FRIDAY NIGHT THROUGH
SATURDAY EVENING...
* WHAT...Moderate to heavy snow possible. Total snow accumulation
of 3 to 8 inches possible. Winds could gust as high as 40 mph.
* WHERE...Litchfield County.
* WHEN...From late Friday night through Saturday evening.
* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult.
* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The best chance for the higher accumulation
will be across southeastern parts of Litchfield County.</description>
<instruction>Monitor the latest forecasts for updates on this situation.</instruction>
